{"tid":537592,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"10萬候鳥抵深圳灣","createTime":"2018-01-22T23:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T07:34:16.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ddcb0dd57e05bde275d9fd1704b09f31219b198d","tid":537592,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/152050/thumbnail/7232e99957705e7e2affdaabf77e2262.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F152050%2Fthumbnail%2F7232e99957705e7e2affdaabf77e2262.jpg&h=595b8ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有「候鳥天堂」之稱的深圳灣目前進入黃金觀鳥期，各種鷺、鷗、雁、鴨聚集於此過冬。深圳灣及跨越深港兩地的大片紅樹林濕地更是候鳥的主要聚集地點，吸引不少市民及攝影發燒友到場觀賞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1148365/xlarge/636585477807934e7355ed4247a73b96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1148365%2Fxlarge%2F636585477807934e7355ed4247a73b96.jpg&h=0fbee81b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不少攝影發燒友大讚深圳灣「候鳥天堂」，並上載候鳥的照片到社交媒體。（微博圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1148382/xlarge/6da784a61e5dfe6ad52955d9f8d7aa8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1148382%2Fxlarge%2F6da784a61e5dfe6ad52955d9f8d7aa8f.jpg&h=83e5d192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1148384/xlarge/f70c1750148faf5f02de62508a2ad3fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1148384%2Fxlarge%2Ff70c1750148faf5f02de62508a2ad3fb.jpg&h=eee1e329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1148383/xlarge/689ca0d8f78be9ffd019bc714f2eaed9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1148383%2Fxlarge%2F689ca0d8f78be9ffd019bc714f2eaed9.jpg&h=60e3821a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1148388/xlarge/5dc1fb199bb39fcd7deb59ea9c3ce38d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1148388%2Fxlarge%2F5dc1fb199bb39fcd7deb59ea9c3ce38d.jpg&h=c0baefd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1148389/xlarge/3f6e9a3b5132dd235ca91a3917ea88c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1148389%2Fxlarge%2F3f6e9a3b5132dd235ca91a3917ea88c1.jpg&h=ff210013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1148386/xlarge/b2202121228a182562bd68b8739c5d95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1148386%2Fxlarge%2Fb2202121228a182562bd68b8739c5d95.jpg&h=babf85e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1148387/xlarge/c2baba8dc82798302ad0698ad863f69f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1148387%2Fxlarge%2Fc2baba8dc82798302ad0698ad863f69f.jpg&h=8c251819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1148391/xlarge/40770e9774ffdfab51ec99a0bd096603.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1148391%2Fxlarge%2F40770e9774ffdfab51ec99a0bd096603.jpg&h=f863a62c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1148390/xlarge/26b2a36dca7bb583874817012be4f634.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1148390%2Fxlarge%2F26b2a36dca7bb583874817012be4f634.jpg&h=83c868b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1148403/xlarge/e807300298a5a52b74ba17b377881978.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1148403%2Fxlarge%2Fe807300298a5a52b74ba17b377881978.jpg&h=11cb18dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國面積最小的國家級自然保護區&mdash;&mdash;「廣東內伶仃&mdash;福田紅樹林國家級自然保護區」近期成為雀鳥天堂。據保護區職員介紹，地球上共有8條候鳥遷徙線路，深圳是候鳥從西伯利亞遷徙至澳洲的重要中轉站。<br />\n<br />\n深圳灣及跨越深港兩地的大片紅樹林濕地，每年冬季都能吸引10萬多隻候鳥在此補充能量，種類更多達189種。每年11月至翌年3月，深圳灣一帶隨處可見候鳥飛騰的畫面，12月及1月更是候鳥抵步的密集時期。<br />\n<br />\n在保護區內，經常還能看到國家Ⅱ級重點保護野生動物黑臉琵鷺。據悉，黑臉琵鷺是極度瀕危候鳥，據2017年（香港觀鳥協會）鳥類調查數據顯示，全球黑臉琵鷺共有3951隻，有375只會在深圳灣過冬，佔全球總數的近十分之一。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/152050/-%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E8%A7%80%E9%B3%A5%E6%9C%9F-10%E8%90%AC%E5%80%99%E9%B3%A5%E6%8A%B5%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E7%81%A3-%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E9%BE%8D%E5%8F%8B%E8%A7%80%E8%B3%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2F152050%2F-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%25A7%2580%25E9%25B3%25A5%25E6%259C%259F-10%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2580%2599%25E9%25B3%25A5%25E6%258A%25B5%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%259C%25B3%25E7%2581%25A3-%25E5%2590%25B8%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%258F%258B%25E8%25A7%2580%25E8%25B3%259E&d=gt6vtea6%2B%2Bv202uvf3dMStr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=1a598ff9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/152050/-%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E8%A7%80%E9%B3%A5%E6%9C%9F-10%E8%90%AC%E5%80%99%E9%B3%A5%E6%8A%B5%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E7%81%A3-%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E9%BE%8D%E5%8F%8B%E8%A7%80%E8%B3%9E</a>"},{"pid":"7cea05c9e30218e1e176705230769647c9069305","tid":537592,"uid":23416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:45:49.000Z","msg":"每日百五隻來港"},{"pid":"636f6b5113c814b8e0fe96740b9330d768a58951","tid":537592,"uid":117729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:50:57.000Z","msg":"香港唔係叫后海灣咩？<br />\n求指正"},{"pid":"ae4f8b40fc09340313898f48cca2c06a38925e18","tid":537592,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cea05c9e30218e1e176705230769647c9069305","tid":537592,"uid":23416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T23:45:49.000Z","msg":"每日百五隻來港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T00:05:18.000Z","msg":"嗰啲係昆蟲"},{"pid":"687ab84bc69226430cd04ae086